Methodology
Framework







Roles
Set of activities, responsibilities, and authorities granted to/performed by a person group or team. Development team, Scrum Master, Product Owner
Rituals
Represent actions to be taken or a specific act of work to be performed. Sprint, Sprint planning, daily scrum, sprint execution, sprint review, sprint retrospective, product backlog grooming
Artifacts
Documents that report, or documentation of some activity that has been performed or is planning to be performed. Definition of done, product backlog, user stories, sprint backlog, burn-down chart, task board
Rules
Rules define a prescribed behavior or a control mechanism that is intended to be followed



